WorkItem.Description:
Admittedly, I'm not that adept with graphics, and I only spent about 30 minutes on this, so I'm not sure if this is the *right* way to do this.
 
I just prototyped a way to embed SVG graphics in WinForms application via the Piccolo.NET toolkit (http://www.cs.umd.edu/hcil/jazz/).  I explained what I did here: http://groups.google.com/group/piccolo2d-users/browse_thread/thread/4332fc25c1109e7d?hl=en
 
It seemed like the renderer was primarily geared towards images, so I added this method to SvgRenderer.  
 
        public static SvgRenderer FromGraphics(Graphics graphics) 
        { 
            SvgRenderer renderer = new SvgRenderer(); 
            renderer._innerGraphics = graphics; 
            return renderer; 
        }
